dbWriteSQLite

output: github_document

Adds additional functionality to dbWriteTable() and dbReadTable() for SQLiteConnection objects

Installation

To install the latest version from the Poisson drat repository

install.packages("drat")
drat::addRepo("poissonconsulting")
install.packages("dbWriteSQLite")
